You are building SmartChapa (Next.js App Router + TypeScript strict).

- Use Portuguese (pt-MZ) for all UI labels.
- Mobile-first UI, minimum 48px touch targets.
- Currency format: "15 MT" (number first, then MT).
- Use Tailwind + shadcn/ui components; cards rounded-xl, inputs rounded-lg.
- Use TanStack Query v5 for all data fetching and mutations.
- Use React Hook Form + Zod for all forms.
- Use Zustand for client-only state (booking flow, session snapshot).
- Supabase: Postgres + Auth + Realtime (except live GPS, which is Firebase RTDB only).

